Source: Lief's Fog by Lief
Use caution, these fog effects will slow the module down to a crawl if too many are used.

Works for both standard and secret trap doors.

For standard, the tag of the waypoint destination must be set to LOC_<tag of door>.

For secret, the waypoint should be set to LOC_<tag of detect trigger>.
Source: All Purpose Placeables 1.1 by M.G.Skaggs Edited by SBird for CEP
